181 3.955L4.55 22.31a2.346 2.346 0 003.955-1.18l.66-3.18c.86.411 1.819.648 2.833.648 3.64 0 6.6-2.96 6.6-6.6a6.537 6.537 0 00-.648-2.832l3.18-.662a2.342 2.342 0 001.77-1.625 2.339 2.339 0 00-.59-2.328" data-v-89b300da data-v-89b300da></path></svg></div><div class="nutrient-name" data-v-89b300da><p data-v-89b300da>糖質</p></div><div class="nutrient-amount" data-v-89b300da><p data-v-89b300da>89.9g</p></div></li><li class="recipe-nutrient" data-v-89b300da><div class="nutrient-icon" data-v-89b300da><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="icon-nutrient" data-v-89b300da data-v-89b300da><path d="M12.002 1c3.73 0 6.767 2.938 6.828 6.57l2.13 12.252a2.673 2.673 0 01-.616 2.211 2.803 2.803 0 01-2.128.966H5.782c-.82 0-1.595-.35-2.125-.965a2.671 2.671 0 01-.617-2.212L5.176 7.535C5.256 3.918 8.285 1 12.002 1zm4.547 7.89H7.451L5.479 20.228a.283.283 0 00.07.244c.04.05.116.108.233.108h12.434a.305.305 0 00.305-.352L16.549 8.89zm-4.63 2.15c1.403 0 2.43.527 2.786 1.438a.96.96 0 01.076.392c0 .422-.315.706-.783.712-.406 0-.661-.144-.88-.493-.238-.448-.646-.622-1.185-.622-.676 0-1.073.299-1.073.72 0 .38.33.588 1.13.737l.752.14c1.567.293 2.278.915 2.278 2.042 0 1.443-1.153 2.359-3.087 2.359-1.592 0-2.553-.588-2.859-1.328a1.132 1.132 0 01-.097-.452c0-.458.337-.766.81-.766.36 0 .605.123.845.482.248.447.741.636 1.332.636.727 0 1.2-.318 1.2-.756 0-.398-.31-.602-1.18-.765l-.758-.14c-1.46-.269-2.223-.97-2.223-2.064 0-1.381 1.227-2.271 2.916-2.271zm.083-7.621A4.341 4.341 0 007.843 6.47h8.317a4.34 4.34 0 00-4.158-3.051z" data-v-89b300da data-v-89b300da></path></svg></div><div class="nutrient-name" data-v-89b300da><p data-v-89b300da>塩分</p></div><div class="nutrient-amount" data-v-89b300da><p data-v-89b300da>2.4g</p></div></li></ul></div><ul class="recipe-description" data-v-89b300da><li data-v-89b300da>※1人分あたり</li><li data-v-89b300da>※費用目安はレシピ全体での金額となります。</li></ul></div><!----><!----><!----></div></div><div class="recipe-content__detail" data-v-73bb50e4><div class="recipe-ingredients" data-v-73bb50e4><div class="delish-recipe-ingredients" data-v-25cf3c40 data-v-73bb50e4><h2 class="ingredient-header text-h2-renewal" data-v-25cf3c40><span class="recipe-serving" data-v-25cf3c40> 材料 <span data-v-25cf3c40>【1人分】</span></span></h2><ul class="ingredient-list" data-v-25cf3c40><!----><li class="ingredient" data-v-25cf3c40><span class="ingredient-name" data-v-25cf3c40>ごはん</span><span class="ingredient-serving" data-v-25cf3c40>どんぶり1杯(200g)</span></li><li class="ingredient" data-v-25cf3c40><a href="/categories/1343" class="ingredient-name" data-v-25cf3c40> 卵 </a><span class="ingredient-serving" data-v-25cf3c40>2個</span></li><li class="ingredient" data-v-25cf3c40><a href="/categories/2775" class="ingredient-name" data-v-25cf3c40> ベーコン </a><span class="ingredient-serving" data-v-25cf3c40>2枚</span></li><li class="ingredient" data-v-25cf3c40><a href="/search?q=%E7%89%9B%E4%B9%B3" class="ingredient-name" data-v-25cf3c40> 牛乳 </a><span class="ingredient-serving" data-v-25cf3c40>大さじ1</span></li><li class="ingredient" data-v-25cf3c40><a href="/categories/2736" class="ingredient-name" data-v-25cf3c40> 玉ねぎ </a><span class="ingredient-serving" data-v-25cf3c40>1/4個(50g)</span></li><li class="ingredient" data-v-25cf3c40><span class="ingredient-name" data-v-25cf3c40>オリーブオイル</span><span class="ingredient-serving" data-v-25cf3c40>大さじ1</span></li><li class="ingredient-group__header" data-v-25cf3c40>☆ケチャップライス調味料</li><li class="ingredient" data-v-25cf3c40><span class="ingredient-name" data-v-25cf3c40>ケチャップ</span><span class="ingredient-serving" data-v-25cf3c40>大さじ1と1/2</span></li><li class="ingredient" data-v-25cf3c40><span class="ingredient-name" data-v-25cf3c40>塩こしょう</span><span class="ingredient-serving" data-v-25cf3c40>少々</span></li><li class="ingredient-group__header" data-v-25cf3c40>仕上げ用</li><li class="ingredient" data-v-25cf3c40><span class="ingredient-name" data-v-25cf3c40>ケチャップ</span><span class="ingredient-serving" data-v-25cf3c40>大さじ1</span></li></ul><div data-v-25cf3c40><a href="https://corp.every.tv/cooking_notes" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="cooking-notice" data-v-25cf3c40><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="icon-info" data-v-25cf3c40><path d="M12 1c6.067 0 11 4.935 11 11s-4.933 11-11 11C5.934 23 1 18.065 1 12S5.934 1 12 1zm0 2.42c-4.731 0-8.581 3.849-8.581 8.58s3.85 8.58 8.581 8.58 8.581-3.849 8.581-8.58S16.731 3.42 12 3.42zm0 6.379c.668 0 1.21.542 1.21 1.21v5.28a1.21 1.21 0 01-2.42 0v-5.28c0-.668.542-1.21 1.21-1.21zm0-3.464a1.21 1.21 0 11-.001 2.421A1.21 1.21 0 0112 6.335z" data-v-25cf3c40></path></svg><span class="text-notice" data-v-25cf3c40>料理を楽しむにあたって</span></a></div></div><div data-v-73bb50e4></div><!----></div><!----><div class="delish-recipe-steps" data-v-13cd9798 data-v-73bb50e4><h2 class="text-h2-renewal recipe-steps-title" data-v-13cd9798>手順</h2><!----><ol class="steps" data-v-13cd9798><li class="step" data-v-13cd9798><div class="delish-recipe-step-item" data-v-2ffab46a data-v-13cd9798><div id="step-video-1" class="step-image-wrap" data-v-2ffab46a><div class="delish-step-player delish-step-player" data-v-642f7b0b data-v-2ffab46a><div class="video-player delish-player-custom-skin" data-v-5513e455 data-v-642f7b0b><video preload="none" poster="https://media.delishkitchen.tv/recipe/482594657587429799/steps/1.jpg?version=1705636835" playsinline="true" webkit-playsinline="true" class="video-js" data-v-5513e455><source src="https://media.delishkitchen.tv/recipe/482594657587429799/steps/1.m3u8" type="application/x-mpegURL" fetchpriority="high" data-v-5513e455></video></div></div></div><p class="step-num" data-v-2ffab46a>1</p><div class="step-text-wrap" data-v-2ffab46a><p class="step-desc" data-v-2ffab46a>玉ねぎはみじん切りにする。</p><!----><!----></div></div></li><li class="step" data-v-13cd9798><div class="delish-recipe-step-item" data-v-2ffab46a data-v-13cd9798><div id="step-video-2" class="step-image-wrap" data-v-2ffab46a><div class="delish-step-player delish-step-player" data-v-642f7b0b data-v-2ffab46a><div class="video-player delish-player-custom-skin" data-v-5513e455 data-v-642f7b0b><video preload="none" poster="https://media.delishkitchen.tv/recipe/482594657587429799/steps/2.jpg?version=1705636835" playsinline="true" webkit-playsinline="true" class="video-js" data-v-5513e455><source src="https://media.delishkitchen.tv/recipe/482594657587429799/steps/2.m3u8" type="application/x-mpegURL" fetchpriority="high" data-v-5513e455></video></div></div></div><p class="step-num" data-v-2ffab46a>2</p><div class="step-text-wrap" data-v-2ffab46a><p class="step-desc" data-v-2ffab46a>ベーコンは5mm幅に切る。</p><!----><!----></div></div></li><li class="step" data-v-13cd9798><div class="delish-recipe-step-item" data-v-2ffab46a data-v-13cd9798><div id="step-video-3" class="step-image-wrap" data-v-2ffab46a><div class="delish-step-player delish-step-player" data-v-642f7b0b data-v-2ffab46a><div class="video-player delish-player-custom-skin" data-v-5513e455 data-v-642f7b0b><video preload="none" poster="https://media.delishkitchen.tv/recipe/482594657587429799/steps/3.jpg?version=1705636835" playsinline="true" webkit-playsinline="true" class="video-js" data-v-5513e455><source src="https://media.delishkitchen.tv/recipe/482594657587429799/steps/3.m3u8" type="application/x-mpegURL" fetchpriority="high" data-v-5513e455></video></div></div></div><p class="step-num" data-v-2ffab46a>3</p><div class="step-text-wrap" data-v-2ffab46a><p class="step-desc" data-v-2ffab46a>ボウルに卵を割り入れ、牛乳を加えて混ぜる(卵液)。</p><!----><!----></div></div></li><li class="step" data-v-13cd9798><div class="delish-recipe-step-item" data-v-2ffab46a data-v-13cd9798><div id="step-video-4" class="step-image-wrap" data-v-2ffab46a><div class="delish-step-player delish-step-player" data-v-642f7b0b data-v-2ffab46a><div class="video-player delish-player-custom-skin" data-v-5513e455 data-v-642f7b0b><video preload="none" poster="https://media.delishkitchen.tv/recipe/482594657587429799/steps/4.jpg?version=1705636835" playsinline="true" webkit-playsinline="true" class="video-js" data-v-5513e455><source src="https://media.delishkitchen.tv/recipe/482594657587429799/steps/4.m3u8" type="application/x-mpegURL" fetchpriority="high" data-v-5513e455></video></div></div></div><p class="step-num" data-v-2ffab46a>4</p><div class="step-text-wrap" data-v-2ffab46a><p class="step-desc" data-v-2ffab46a>フライパンにオリーブオイルの半量(大さじ1/2)を入れて熱し、玉ねぎを入れてしんなりとするまで炒める。ベーコンを加えてさっと炒める。</p><!----><div class="point-wrap" data-v-2ffab46a><p class="title" data-v-2ffab46a>ポイント</p><p class="point" data-v-2ffab46a> コクのあるオムライスにしたい場合はオリーブオイルをバターに変更していただいてもおいしくいただけます。 </p></div></div></div></li><li class="step" data-v-13cd9798><div class="delish-recipe-step-item" data-v-2ffab46a data-v-13cd9798><div id="step-video-5" class="step-image-wrap" data-v-2ffab46a><div class="delish-step-player delish-step-player" data-v-642f7b0b data-v-2ffab46a><div class="video-player delish-player-custom-skin" data-v-5513e455 data-v-642f7b0b><video preload="none" poster="https://media.delishkitchen.tv/recipe/482594657587429799/steps/5.jpg?version=1705636835" playsinline="true" webkit-playsinline="true" class="video-js" data-v-5513e455><source src="https://media.delishkitchen.tv/recipe/482594657587429799/steps/5.m3u8" type="application/x-mpegURL" fetchpriority="high" data-v-5513e455></video></div></div></div><p class="step-num" data-v-2ffab46a>5</p><div class="step-text-wrap" data-v-2ffab46a><p class="step-desc" data-v-2ffab46a>ケチャップ(大さじ1と1/2)を加えて30秒〜1分ほど炒め、ごはんを加えて炒め合わせる。塩こしょうを加えて味をととのえ、器に盛る。</p><!----><div class="point-wrap" data-v-2ffab46a><p class="title" data-v-2ffab46a>ポイント</p><p class="point" data-v-2ffab46a> あたたかいごはんを使いましょう。 </p></div></div></div></li><li class="step" data-v-13cd9798><div class="delish-recipe-step-item" data-v-2ffab46a data-v-13cd9798><div id="step-video-6" class="step-image-wrap" data-v-2ffab46a><div class="delish-step-player delish-step-player" data-v-642f7b0b data-v-2ffab46a><div class="video-player delish-player-custom-skin" data-v-5513e455 data-v-642f7b0b><video preload="none" poster="https://media.delishkitchen.tv/recipe/482594657587429799/steps/6.jpg?version=1705636835" playsinline="true" webkit-playsinline="true" class="video-js" data-v-5513e455><source src="https://media.delishkitchen.tv/recipe/482594657587429799/steps/6.m3u8" type="application/x-mpegURL" fetchpriority="high" data-v-5513e455></video></div></div></div><p class="step-num" data-v-2ffab46a>6</p><div class="step-text-wrap" data-v-2ffab46a><p class="step-desc" data-v-2ffab46a>フライパンは洗って水気をふきとる。残りのオリーブオイル(大さじ1/2)を入れて中火で熱し、卵液を流し入れる。菜箸で大きくかき混ぜながら半熟状になるまで加熱する。</p><!----><!----></div></div></li><li class="step" data-v-13cd9798><div class="delish-recipe-step-item" data-v-2ffab46a data-v-13cd9798><div id="step-video-7" class="step-image-wrap" data-v-2ffab46a><div class="delish-step-player delish-step-player" data-v-642f7b0b data-v-2ffab46a><div class="video-player delish-player-custom-skin" data-v-5513e455 data-v-642f7b0b><video preload="none" poster="https://media.delishkitchen.tv/recipe/482594657587429799/steps/7.jpg?version=1705636835" playsinline="true" webkit-playsinline="true" class="video-js" data-v-5513e455><source src="https://media.delishkitchen.tv/recipe/482594657587429799/steps/7.m3u8" type="application/x-mpegURL" fetchpriority="high" data-v-5513e455></video></div></div></div><p class="step-num" data-v-2ffab46a>7</p><div class="step-text-wrap" data-v-2ffab46a><p class="step-desc" data-v-2ffab46a>5の器に卵を盛る。ケチャップをかける。</p><!----><!----></div></div></li></ol></div></div><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><div id="delish-recipe-top-summary-cooking-reports" class="delish-recipe-top-summary-cooking-reports" data-v-08998891 data-v-73bb50e4><h2 class="title text-h2-renewal" data-v-08998891>レビュー</h2><div class="delish-cooking-reports-top-summary" data-v-28d67760 data-v-08998891><div class="review-stars" data-v-28d67760><div class="delish-recipe-review-stars" data-v-86131886 data-v-28d67760><div class="delish-recipe-review-star" data-v-86131886><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="icon icon-star y